              <li><a href="https://www.midviewk12.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Midview Local Schools</a> ‚Äî Grafton, Eaton Twp, Carlisle Twp</li>
              <li><a href="https://www.keystonelocalschools.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Keystone Local Schools</a> ‚Äî LaGrange</li>
              <li><a href="https://www.oberlinschools.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Oberlin City Schools</a> ‚Äî Oberlin</li>
